messages.message: If you filter the apps listed here https://aihub.instabase.com/hub?tab=Organization to just chatbots, those should be fair game to index. In some cases, we can consider asking the creator to include the data source directly to Search (eg: HR docs must be coming from confluence) but in some cases the docs are manually uploaded (eg: AI Hub docs) and can be added to search to make it more useful
Thanks Avi, reached with DM on more details on which chatbots we need to pull amongst all published ones.
